              <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="dd:3;129:19">Exits with code <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="codeph:4;129:43">1</codeph> if any Required rule fails,
              marking the GitHub check as failed and blocking the merge.</dd>
            </dlentry>
            <dlentry class="- topic/dlentry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="dlentry:4;132:22">
