              <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="dd:4;134:19"><codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;134:27">if: always()</codeph> ensures the upload runs even
