            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="li:6;152:17"><codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_integrate-github-actions.dita" xtrc="codeph:8;152:25">rules/tutorial.json</codeph> — the path to your team's
